    "summary": "Channel workload + Kong-route names are built directly via `printf \"web-%s\"/\"functions-%s\" $c.name` without invoking `pawtograder.channel.host`, so the DNS-1123 name validation in the helper is bypassed for the Deployment/Service/Kong objects; validation only runs when ingress.enabled is true (ingress-channels.yaml) or via kong-config.",
